{"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"category":"Orange Unified Design System","categoryPathComponent":"Table-Of-Contents-(discovery)","title":"Swift Package Discovery Tutorial","estimatedTime":"2hr 5min","role":"overview"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/Table-Of-Contents-(discovery)"},"kind":"overview","hierarchy":{"reference":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/Table-Of-Contents-(discovery)","paths":[]},"sections":[{"image":"ic_unified_ds.png","action":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-1-package-and-librairies","overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Get started"}],"isActive":true,"overridingTitle":"Get started","type":"reference"},"kind":"hero","title":"Swift Package Discovery Tutorial","backgroundImage":"ic_unified_ds.png","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Discovering a new framework can be exciting and scary. Learn how you can embed and use OUDS Swift Package."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"With this tutorial you will learn fundamental concepts of Orange Unified Design System and discover the layers of this framework."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Theme, components, tokens… everything will be introduced!","type":"text"}]}]},{"image":null,"kind":"volume","content":[],"chapters":[{"tutorials":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-1-package-and-librairies"],"name":"Import of the Swift Package and choose its librairies","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In this chapter you will learn how to import the OUDS iOS Swift Package and which librairies it provides","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"you should choose for your needs.","type":"text"}]}],"image":"ic_unified_ds.png"},{"tutorials":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-2-instanciate-theme"],"name":"Preparation of the theme","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In this chapter you will see how to instanciate a theme and inject it inside your app","type":"text"}]}],"image":"ic_theme_intro.png"},{"name":"Use of first components provided by OUDS","tutorials":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-3-use-first-components"],"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In this chapter you will see how you can use your first components provided by OUDS Swift Package"}]}],"image":"ic_component_intro.png"},{"tutorials":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-4-use-other-components"],"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In this chapter you will use original components of OUDS and richer ones","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"image":"ic_component_intro.png","name":"Richer and more original components of OUDS"},{"tutorials":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-5-styling-things"],"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"OUDS is not only about components and themes. It provides view modifiers, typographies and tokens which can be used. You will learn how.","type":"text"}]}],"image":"ic_design_token_intro.png","name":"Typography, view modifiers and tokens"},{"name":"Go further with more ressources","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You can have questions and issues, and there are resources online. Let’s see that together.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"tutorials":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-6-going-further"],"image":"ic_unified_ds.png"}],"name":null}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/tutorials\/table-of-contents-(discovery)"]}],"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesContract/tutorials/OUDSThemesContract/tutorial-discovery-4-use-other-components":{"title":"Add more OUDS com