ll be introduced!"}],"title":"Swift Package Discovery Tutorial","url":"\/tutorials\/table-of-contents-(discovery)","role":"overview","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/Table-Of-Contents-(discovery)","type":"topic","kind":"overview"},"ic_unified_ds.png":{"identifier":"ic_unified_ds.png","type":"image","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesContract\/ic_unified_ds.png"}],"alt":"Logo of OUDS"},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/tutorials/OUDSThemesContract/tutorial-discovery-1-package-and-librairies":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDS iOS is exposed through an open source Swift Package hosted on GitHub, and provides several librairies for your needs."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"These librairies help to split products and make users able to select only what they need.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"SwiftUI is the only official supported framework for Apple platforms."}],"estimatedTime":"10min","kind":"project","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-1-package-and-librairies","type":"topic","url":"\/tutorials\/oudsthemescontract\/tutorial-discovery-1-package-and-librairies","role":"project","title":"Swift Package integration"}}}